OL,4,CAlgerian author Said Djabelkhir
OL,5,Csentenced to jail for offending Islam
OL,6, An author of Islamic books in Algeria
OL,7, has been sentenced to three years in
OL,8, prison for offending the religion.
OL,10,FSaid Djabelkhir said he was surprised
OL,11,Fby the severity of the sentence he had
OL,12,Fbeen given and would appeal.
OL,14,FHe was tried after seven lawyers and a
OL,15,Ffellow academic lodged complaints
OL,16,Fagainst him for disrespecting Islam.
OL,18,FMr Djabelkhir had said the animal
OL,19,Fsacrifice during the Muslim festival of
OL,20,FEid was based on a pre-Islamic pagan
OL,21,Fritual.
